{"word":"οἴκοι","slug":"οἴκοι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>οἴκοι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:οἶκος'><el>οἶκος</el></a>\n<p/><i>at home, in the house</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>domi</el>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>τὰ οἴκοι</el> one's <i>domestic affairs</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; so, <el>ἡ οἴκοι δίαιτα</el> <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>; <el>ἡ οἴκοι</el> (<a href='S:scilicet'>sc.</a> <el>πόλις</el>) <i>one's own country</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/>"}]}